    "\n",
    "**Goal:** simulate one configured emitter and inspect its state traces.\n",
    "\n",
    "Main objects:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `Configuration`\n",
    "- emitter preset\n",
    "- runtime settings\n",
    "- simulated voltage/state output\n"
   ],
